Natalia Nogulich https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natalia_Nogulich 0 Natalia Nogulich (born October 1, 1950) is an American film and television actress. Nogulich was born Natalija Nogulich in Chicago, Illinois, of Serbian descent. Her best-known appearances have been on Star Trek: The Next Generation and Star Trek: Deep Space Nine as Vice Admiral/Fleet Admiral Alynna Nechayev. She portrayed Josephine Hoffa in the film Hoffa and provided the voice for Mon Mothma for the radio adaptation of Return of the Jedi.
